HEADWORD: Hyetograph
<hw>Hy"e*to*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ rain +
<ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <def>A chart or graphic representation of the
average distribution of rain over the surface of the earth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

